{"tid":585113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行人後面 前面條友成日好驚我咁","createTime":"2018-03-08T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T10:38:44.000Z","uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e236d8790c64452c8fecc4ad19e816d8a819dcf4","tid":585113,"uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"前面有個普通陌生人<br />\n我只係好普通咁岩行佢後面<br />\n但係前面個條友成日有防備signal 咁<br />\n會扮野望左望右/突登扮搵下背狼/停係度/向後望（其實係驚我係賊仔？定唔知驚乜）<br />\n無論我腳步係靜音or有鎖時聲都係咁or友腳步聲<br />\n唔知點解 好多陌生人都係咁<br />\n點解會咁？有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21b91bc85537e926b6799b9d5fc61f495e1deff","tid":585113,"uid":104135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"行快兩步過咗佢唔得咩"},{"pid":"ab265fa267d4adcbcb7ad2940908659c4fe15507","tid":585113,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"下次試下後面有人 你做同樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954ed5440d8ea7464c2aabd40d59bca6cf7f3974","tid":585113,"uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"我已經成日刻意示意我係正常人已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a738a99f10e6e263cab9190ad8684c45077fe6dd","tid":585113,"uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab265fa267d4adcbcb7ad2940908659c4fe15507","tid":585113,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"下次試下後面有人 你做同樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"我平時都唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d467fb837b57e617cad1c3aa3e4b70ae4f5b19a","tid":585113,"uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21b91bc85537e926b6799b9d5fc61f495e1deff","tid":585113,"uid":104135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci