score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"難本上行邊都會咁 遇咩人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a838672e0ff1c3b3f1558a05bba30dffecd78f0","tid":585113,"uid":78222,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"我都成日俾人望 明明係d廢老係前面塞住條路<br />\n我行快d過佢前面 佢會以為我偷野咁望一望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班廢老唔塞住條路未唔洗望黎望去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984e29cc99225167c294ed00404884c543b1a519","tid":585113,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"成日行街, 後面總有D友仔好急好急, 急到踩到我隻腳踭.  比人踩完, 通常我會停係度等佢地過頭, 然後掉住佢地尾, 跟住佢地就會好驚我報復, 然後急急步走, 見到有地方就會閃埋一邊.  根本大部份係條街行前面既人都係心虛, 求其試下佢地, 就知佢地平時都驚青到死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1128d8ecdf92e1243f20b9bb8a66e5046f17582c","tid":585113,"uid":139617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8d93cf95e9fae2372148de8437cde1a45364bad","tid":585113,"uid":150488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7203c021ca134786edf3527d2269779ccc73a30","tid":585113,"uid":139617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想講好耐 以為得我一個係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"你行路係咪靜音"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"應該係 冇留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢地望過黎果時我唔會望住佢地 然後加快步伐咁行過佢"},{"pid":"8ead1aa216b133a987728c03daf72907ccb54975","tid":585113,"uid":139617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1128d8ecdf92e1243f20b9bb8a66e5046f17582c","tid":585113,"uid":139617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote"